## Verification
1. Start a new game and confirm deck has exactly 54 cards (Star has 7, Cross/Square have 9, Circle/Triangle have 12, plus 5 Whot)
2. Play card 1 → verify the same player's hand is still interactive
3. Play card 8 → verify the next player is skipped
4. Play card 14 → verify all players pick a card including the player who played it, then that player plays again
5. Play card 2 → if opponent has a 2 and defend is enabled, they can play it; otherwise they draw 2
6. Test stacking: two 2s played in sequence → the next player must draw 4
